text: Schulte is an unincorporated community in Sedgwick County, Kansas, United States. ==History== Schulte started because the Orient railway went through there. Schulte had a post office. It opened in 1906. It closed in 1934. ==References== ==Other websites== * Sedgwick County Maps: Current , Historic , KDOT Category:Unincorporated communities in Sedgwick County, Kansas
title: Schulte, Kansas
